Day 2 | Session 2
Task 2: Creating users and assigning roles in Microsoft Entra ID

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Steps to create a resource group and assign roles to the user:
Step 1: In navigation bar click on "Resource Group" and click on "CREATE" to create new Resource Group.
Step 2: Enter Resource Group name and Select the Region.
Step 3: Then Click on "REVIEW+CREATE" and click on "CREATE" option which is located at bottom left corner.
Step 4: View Resource Group which you created and in that select "Access Control [IAM]".
Step 5: Click on Add and select "Add Assign Role" and select the role which you want to assign. And select "REVIEW+ASSIGN".
Step 6: Select the user.
Step 7: Role will be assigned to the selected user.

